Authors@R: c(person("Antonin", "Caussin", email = "antonin.caussin@student.uliege.be", role = c("aut", "cre")), person(given = NA, family = "Université de Liège - Département d'enseignement AGRO BIO-TECH", role = "cph"), person("Gauthier", "Ligot", email = "gligot@uliege.be", role = "aut"))
Description: Estimation of timber volume, biomass, and forest carbon stock based on existing allometric equations.  The package provides automated calculations  
